level.text: A nurse-practitioner shall practice in accordance with §§ 604 and 606 of the Act, D.C. Code §§ 2-3306.4 and 2-3306.7 (1988).

level.heading: SOURCE
level.text: Final Rulemaking published at 36 DCR 3505, 3508 (May 12, 1989); as amended by Final Rulemaking published at 49 DCR 11751 (December 27, 2002).
